{"tid":1467000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚一役 真係輸撚晒","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:45.000Z","uid":58412,"like":54,"dislike":104,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"b1eee33dfa977d312d439b6a0fdfe103065a00d3","tid":1467000,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:13.000Z","msg":"今晚一役 真係輸撚晒 <br />\n簡簡單單混幾隻爛頭卒入嚟 <br />\n適時畀班黑警喬裝嘅鬼踢爆 <br />\n帶頭挑起大家情緒 <br />\n要打要殺 要動私刑咁<br />\n四方八面記者鏡頭 全世界影晒<br />\nSpin晒去捉鬼打鬼嘅場口 <br />\n和理非主場完全淪陷 <br />\n勇武進場？ <br />\n未算 勇武有幾可會打FA打記者 <br />\n鄉黑嘅公仔佬 金毛MK 鬼到周圍辣火頭嘅黑警 呢班先係今晚嘅主角 <br />\n但係就無一個前線冷靜到落嚟睇清個環境發生緊咩事。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfNfTgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfNfTgW.png&h=f67dbe60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"7c13220b221a10296fc82435cd0bccb33dc6cf41","tid":1467000,"uid":187387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[文宣] 公安單野..........<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDChtS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDChtS</a>"},{"pid":"f5f113d1714588c64f125330f2529c6bac13bf1e","tid":1467000,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee914e4efd23b0e4c0e7a0ef74f7023fba7054c","tid":1467000,"uid":24013,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"唔覺邊忽輸，有兩件公安，一件藍t人，再阻到機場飛。<br />\n三毛又想夜晚帶風向，屌你老母"},{"pid":"3ac08a14592f588b3ac2d3589467c928cc1438f2","tid":1467000,"uid":155818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"我知大家嗰晚好嬲<br />\n但發洩哂係阻塞旅客同嗰幾隻大陸仔身上真係唔好睇<br />\n最尾仲有隻金毛怒屌記者救護同前線<br />\n完全唔知佢做乜"},{"pid":"1244040705e7f99eb57d94000cd1edaf8ec1e5b1","tid":1467000,"uid":141328,"like":0,"disli